%h1.page-header About

%p.lead <a href="http://www.thisyeari.com">THISYEARI.COM</a> is a website that challenges you to set one quantifiable goal to reach by the end of the year.

%p.lead Once you set your goal you'll see a dashboard showing your current status. As you update your progress the dashboard updates stats showing where you are versus where you should be at various dates. Use this data to stay motivated and not fall behind!

%p.lead What are you waiting for? <a href="/users/sign_in">Sign up</a> now and get started on making yourself and the world a better place!
/%p.lead From your dashboard you will see <b>four</b> sets of data points based on expected progress by a certain date. The four sets are <b>By Yesterday</b>, <b>By Today</b>, <b>By the End of the Week</b>, and <b>By the End of the Month</b>. The data points show your current progress vs. expected progress.